  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare in a prospective randomised way the effect of two different immunosuppressive
      regimens - mTOR-based regimen or CNI-based regimen - on the progression of coronary artery
      calcification in renal transplant patients measured at baseline, 1, 2, and 3 years after
      transplantation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
