  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>change in coronary artery calcification score</measure>
    <time_frame>3 years</time_frame>
    <description>Comparison in a randomised way the effect of a calcineurin-based immunosuppressive regimen with an mTOR-based regimen on progression of coronary calcification on renal transplant patients.
The results of this study will provide more insight in protection against cardiovascular disease in renal transplant patients.</description>
